datasets.name: dataset_19
queryLines: SELECT `Home Tile` AS `Home Tile`, MEASURE(`Unique Tile Views`) AS `Unique Tile Views`, MEASURE(`Unique Tile Clicks`) AS `Unique Tile Clicks`, MEASURE(`Unique Interstitial Views`) AS `Unique Interstitial Views`, MEASURE(`Unique Interstitial Primary Button Clicks`) AS `Unique Interstitial Primary Button Clicks`, MEASURE(`Unique Interstitial Secondary Button Clicks`) AS `Unique Interstitial Secondary Button Clicks`, (MEASURE(`Unique Tile Clicks`) / MEASURE(`Unique Tile Views`)) * 100 AS `f_ctr`, (MEASURE(`Unique Interstitial Primary Button Clicks`) / MEASURE(`Unique Interstitial Views`)) * 100 AS `f_ctr_cta1`, (MEASURE(`Unique Interstitial Secondary Button Clicks`) / MEASURE(`Unique Interstitial Views`)) * 100 AS `f_ctr_cta0` FROM `workspace.default.hpx_events_model_homepage_summary` ORDER BY `f_ctr_cta0` DESC

fields.name: f_ctr_cta1
fields.expression: (MEASURE(`Unique Interstitial Primary Button Clicks`) / MEASURE(`Unique Interstitial Views`)) * 100

fields.name: f_ctr_cta0
fields.expression: (MEASURE(`Unique Interstitial Secondary Button Clicks`) / MEASURE(`Unique Interstitial Views`)) * 100
